sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)
    participant PM as PlanningManager
    participant PA as PlanAccess
    participant R as Repository (Git)

    Note over C,R: CreateKeyResult
    C->>A: CreateKeyResult(parentObjId, description, startValue, targetValue)
    A->>PM: CreateKeyResult(parentObjId, description, startValue, targetValue)
    PM->>PM: Validate startValue <= targetValue
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findObjectiveByID() [tree-walk]
    PM->>PM: Append new KeyResult to objective
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>PA: ensureThemeIDs() [generate KR ID]
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM->>PA: GetThemes() [re-read for generated ID]
    PM-->>A: *KeyResult
    A-->>C: *KeyResult (Wails DTO)

    Note over C,R: UpdateKeyResult
    C->>A: UpdateKeyResult(keyResultId, description)
    A->>PM: UpdateKeyResult(keyResultId, description)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findKeyResultParent() [tree-walk]
    PM->>PM: Update description
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: UpdateKeyResultProgress
    C->>A: UpdateKeyResultProgress(keyResultId, currentValue)
    A->>PM: UpdateKeyResultProgress(keyResultId, currentValue)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findKeyResultParent() [tree-walk]
    PM->>PM: Update currentValue
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: DeleteKeyResult
    C->>A: DeleteKeyResult(keyResultId)
    A->>PM: DeleteKeyResult(keyResultId)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findKeyResultParent() [tree-walk]
    PM->>PM: Remove KR from parent objective
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil

    Note over C,R: SetKeyResultStatus
    C->>A: SetKeyResultStatus(keyResultId, status)
    A->>PM: SetKeyResultStatus(keyResultId, status)
    PM->>PA: GetThemes()
    PM->>PM: findKeyResultParent() [tree-walk]
    PM->>PM: validateOKRStatusTransition(current, new)
    PM->>PM: Update KR status
    PM->>PA: SaveTheme(modifiedTheme)
    PA->>R: Begin() -> Stage() -> Commit()
    PM-->>A: nil
    A-->>C: nil
